{
  "lesson": "WC-06-01",
  "audioMaster": "training/module06-analytics/WC-06-01-full-narration-v1.0.mp3",
  "audioDurationS": 204.931,
  "method": "silencedetect -32dB/0.28s within known block windows; proportional fallback",
  "phrases": [
    {
      "block": "s01",
      "id": "p01",
      "text": "This is the screen WashCentral opens to.",
      "startS": 0,
      "endS": 2.703,
      "timing": "silence"
    },
    {
      "block": "s01",
      "id": "p02",
      "text": "The Executive Dashboard is the whole network on one page.",
      "startS": 3.066,
      "endS": 6.524,
      "timing": "silence"
    },
    {
      "block": "s01",
      "id": "p03",
      "text": "Before you ever open a ticket or a single site,",
      "startS": 6.985,
      "endS": 9.606,
      "timing": "silence"
    },
    {
      "block": "s01",
      "id": "p04",
      "text": "this is where you check the pulse of the business.",
      "startS": 9.986,
      "endS": 12.182,
      "timing": "silence"
    },
    {
      "block": "s01",
      "id": "p05",
      "text": "Learn to read it quickly,",
      "startS": 12.684,
      "endS": 13.836,
      "timing": "silence"
    },
    {
      "block": "s01",
      "id": "p06",
      "text": "because a lot of support calls start with a number that lives right here.",
      "startS": 14.145,
      "endS": 17.893,
      "timing": "silence"
    },
    {
      "block": "s02",
      "id": "p07",
      "text": "Read the band up top.",
      "startS": 18.32,
      "endS": 19.57,
      "timing": "silence"
    },
    {
      "block": "s02",
      "id": "p08",
      "text": "Network, April, month to date.",
      "startS": 20.604,
      "endS": 21.16,
      "timing": "silence"
    },
    {
      "block": "s02",
      "id": "p09",
      "text": "Every card below rolls all your locations into one figure,",
      "startS": 21.456,
      "endS": 23.059,
      "timing": "silence"
    },
    {
      "block": "s02",
      "id": "p10",
      "text": "so what you see is the business as a whole, not any single wash.",
      "startS": 23.811,
      "endS": 27.374,
      "timing": "silence"
    },
    {
      "block": "s02",
      "id": "p11",
      "text": "The location selector in the header is what narrows it when you need one site.",
      "startS": 27.758,
      "endS": 36.24,
      "timing": "silence"
    },
    {
      "block": "s03",
      "id": "p12",
      "text": "Now find the period row on the right.",
      "startS": 36.64,
      "endS": 38.795,
      "timing": "silence"
    },
    {
      "block": "s03",
      "id": "p13",
      "text": "Today, Week, Month, Quarter, Y-T-D, one year.",
      "startS": 39.303,
      "endS": 39.792,
      "timing": "silence"
    },
    {
      "block": "s03",
      "id": "p14",
      "text": "It is set to Month.",
      "startS": 40.127,
      "endS": 40.521,
      "timing": "silence"
    },
    {
      "block": "s03",
      "id": "p15",
      "text": "That one choice decides the window every card and panel reports on,",
      "startS": 40.909,
      "endS": 41.337,
      "timing": "silence"
    },
    {
      "block": "s03",
      "id": "p16",
      "text": "so always check it before you trust a number.",
      "startS": 41.681,
      "endS": 52.695,
      "timing": "silence"
    },
    {
      "block": "s04",
      "id": "p17",
      "text": "Click through the periods, one at a time.",
      "startS": 53.12,
      "endS": 55.963,
      "timing": "proportional"
    },
    {
      "block": "s04",
      "id": "p18",
      "text": "Watch the numbers redraw for today, then the week, then the quarter, then the year.",
      "startS": 55.963,
      "endS": 60.946,
      "timing": "proportional"
    },
    {
      "block": "s04",
      "id": "p19",
      "text": "Nothing is edited.",
      "startS": 60.946,
      "endS": 61.846,
      "timing": "proportional"
    },
    {
      "block": "s04",
      "id": "p20",
      "text": "You are only changing the lens, and landing back on Month puts it right where it started.",
      "startS": 61.846,
      "endS": 66.943,
      "timing": "proportional"
    },
    {
      "block": "s05",
      "id": "p21",
      "text": "Start with the first three cards.",
      "startS": 67.36,
      "endS": 69.163,
      "timing": "silence"
    },
    {
      "block": "s05",
      "id": "p22",
      "text": "Revenue, cars washed, active members.",
      "startS": 69.755,
      "endS": 70.371,
      "timing": "silence"
    },
    {
      "block": "s05",
      "id": "p23",
      "text": "These are your scale numbers,",
      "startS": 70.623,
      "endS": 71.422,
      "timing": "silence"
    },
    {
      "block": "s05",
      "id": "p24",
      "text": "each with its change against the month before and a small trend line.",
      "startS": 71.728,
      "endS": 72.606,
      "timing": "silence"
    },
    {
      "block": "s05",
      "id": "p25",
      "text": "Green arrows mean the network is growing,",
      "startS": 73.03,
      "endS": 78.179,
      "timing": "silence"
    },
    {
      "block": "s05",
      "id": "p26",
      "text": "and growth in members is the one that quietly lifts the other two.",
      "startS": 78.74,
      "endS": 84.32,
      "timing": "silence"
    },
    {
      "block": "s06",
      "id": "p27",
      "text": "Now the next three.",
      "startS": 84.72,
      "endS": 86.43,
      "timing": "proportional"
    },
    {
      "block": "s06",
      "id": "p28",
      "text": "Conversion rate, visit frequency, and labor percent.",
      "startS": 86.43,
      "endS": 88.349,
      "timing": "proportional"
    },
    {
      "block": "s06",
      "id": "p29",
      "text": "Labor is the one to watch.",
      "startS": 88.349,
      "endS": 90.529,
      "timing": "proportional"
    },
    {
      "block": "s06",
      "id": "p30",
      "text": "It has gone amber because it is running over the fifteen percent target,",
      "startS": 90.529,
      "endS": 94.309,
      "timing": "proportional"
    },
    {
      "block": "s06",
      "id": "p31",
      "text": "and that color is the dashboard flagging it for you.",
      "startS": 94.309,
      "endS": 97.051,
      "timing": "proportional"
    },
    {
      "block": "s06",
      "id": "p32",
      "text": "When you see amber, that is your cue to look at which site is pulling it up.",
      "startS": 97.051,
      "endS": 102.178,
      "timing": "proportional"
    },
    {
      "block": "s07",
      "id": "p33",
      "text": "Drop to the big panel.",
      "startS": 102.64,
      "endS": 104.05,
      "timing": "silence"
    },
    {
      "block": "s07",
      "id": "p34",
      "text": "Twelve months of revenue, stacked by where it came from: memberships, pay per wash, and retail.",
      "startS": 105.038,
      "endS": 108.192,
      "timing": "silence"
    },
    {
      "block": "s07",
      "id": "p35",
      "text": "The membership band is the thick one at the base.",
      "startS": 108.64,
      "endS": 111.174,
      "timing": "silence"
    },
    {
      "block": "s07",
      "id": "p36",
      "text": "That is the recurring money you want climbing, month after month.",
      "startS": 112.131,
      "endS": 118.298,
      "timing": "silence"
    },
    {
      "block": "s08",
      "id": "p37",
      "text": "On the right, every site in one list.",
      "startS": 118.863,
      "endS": 119.513,
      "timing": "silence"
    },
    {
      "block": "s08",
      "id": "p38",
      "text": "Revenue, cars, labor, and how close each runs to its conversion target.",
      "startS": 119.761,
      "endS": 121.343,
      "timing": "silence"
    },
    {
      "block": "s08",
      "id": "p39",
      "text": "The dots and the numbers slide from green toward red as a site slips.",
      "startS": 121.748,
      "endS": 126.744,
      "timing": "silence"
    },
    {
      "block": "s08",
      "id": "p40",
      "text": "One look tells you Naples Coast is the one to check on today,",
      "startS": 127.235,
      "endS": 131.395,
      "timing": "silence"
    },
    {
      "block": "s08",
      "id": "p41",
      "text": "and it saves you scanning six separate reports to find it.",
      "startS": 131.915,
      "endS": 138.256,
      "timing": "silence"
    },
    {
      "block": "s09",
      "id": "p42",
      "text": "Keep going to the members panel.",
      "startS": 138.771,
      "endS": 140.433,
      "timing": "proportional"
    },
    {
      "block": "s09",
      "id": "p43",
      "text": "A line for how many members you have,",
      "startS": 140.433,
      "endS": 143.196,
      "timing": "proportional"
    },
    {
      "block": "s09",
      "id": "p44",
      "text": "against bars for the ones you gained and the ones you lost, month by month.",
      "startS": 143.196,
      "endS": 148.12,
      "timing": "proportional"
    },
    {
      "block": "s09",
      "id": "p45",
      "text": "The gap between those bars is what grows or shrinks the base over time.",
      "startS": 148.12,
      "endS": 151.997,
      "timing": "proportional"
    },
    {
      "block": "s10",
      "id": "p46",
      "text": "Beside it, the revenue mix.",
      "startS": 152.4,
      "endS": 154.186,
      "timing": "silence"
    },
    {
      "block": "s10",
      "id": "p47",
      "text": "A single donut for how this month's money splits apart.",
      "startS": 154.624,
      "endS": 157.701,
      "timing": "silence"
    },
    {
      "block": "s10",
      "id": "p48",
      "text": "It is the quick shape of where revenue is coming from right now,",
      "startS": 158.18,
      "endS": 161.504,
      "timing": "silence"
    },
    {
      "block": "s10",
      "id": "p49",
      "text": "before you go digging for detail.",
      "startS": 161.726,
      "endS": 163.44,
      "timing": "silence"
    },
    {
      "block": "s11",
      "id": "p50",
      "text": "Click the Revenue card.",
      "startS": 163.84,
      "endS": 165.131,
      "timing": "silence"
    },
    {
      "block": "s11",
      "id": "p51",
      "text": "It opens a page just for revenue:",
      "startS": 166.101,
      "endS": 168.045,
      "timing": "silence"
    },
    {
      "block": "s11",
      "id": "p52",
      "text": "today's take, the average ticket, the member share, add-ons, and a table by location.",
      "startS": 168.404,
      "endS": 169.162,
      "timing": "silence"
    },
    {
      "block": "s11",
      "id": "p53",
      "text": "So the cards are not dead ends.",
      "startS": 169.446,
      "endS": 171.394,
      "timing": "silence"
    },
    {
      "block": "s11",
      "id": "p54",
      "text": "Any one of them is a door to the next level of detail.",
      "startS": 171.681,
      "endS": 179.6,
      "timing": "silence"
    },
    {
      "block": "s12",
      "id": "p55",
      "text": "Click Back to Executive Dashboard.",
      "startS": 180,
      "endS": 182.02,
      "timing": "silence"
    },
    {
      "block": "s12",
      "id": "p56",
      "text": "You return to the full scorecard, still on Month, exactly as you left it.",
      "startS": 183.148,
      "endS": 187.36,
      "timing": "silence"
    },
    {
      "block": "s13",
      "id": "p57",
      "text": "That is the whole dashboard.",
      "startS": 187.76,
      "endS": 189.318,
      "timing": "proportional"
    },
    {
      "block": "s13",
      "id": "p58",
      "text": "Pick a period, read the six cards for scale and health,",
      "startS": 189.318,
      "endS": 193.746,
      "timing": "proportional"
    },
    {
      "block": "s13",
      "id": "p59",
      "text": "then the panels for the trend, the sites, your members, and the mix.",
      "startS": 193.746,
      "endS": 197.797,
      "timing": "proportional"
    },
    {
      "block": "s13",
      "id": "p60",
      "text": "It edits nothing, and every card can take you deeper.",
      "startS": 197.797,
      "endS": 200.914,
      "timing": "proportional"
    },
    {
      "block": "s13",
      "id": "p61",
      "text": "Start your day here, then go where the numbers point.",
      "startS": 200.914,
      "endS": 204.424,
      "timing": "proportional"
    }
  ]
}